  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lewys</b> and its variants are a common male name in Westeros. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewys_the_Fishwife\" title=\"Lewys the Fishwife\">Lewys the Fishwife</a>, a man sworn to Dragonstone</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewys_Lydden\" title=\"Lewys Lydden\">Lewys Lydden</a>, Lord of the Deep Den</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewys_Piper\" title=\"Lewys Piper\">Lewys Piper</a>, a squire to Jaime Lannister</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lewys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewis_Lanster\" title=\"Lewis Lanster\">Lewis Lanster</a>, a sellsword archer with the Windblown</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lew\" title=\"Lew\">Lew</a> (disambiguation)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403163023\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14717-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403163023 and revision id 323572\n -->\n",
